
Overview of noun gesture

The noun gesture has 3 senses (first 3 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (20) gesture -- (motion of hands or body to emphasize or help to express a thought or feeling)
2. (4) gesture, motion -- (the use of movements (especially of the hands) to communicate familiar or prearranged signals)
3. (3) gesture -- (something done as an indication of intention; "a political gesture"; "a gesture of defiance")

Overview of verb gesture

The verb gesture has 1 sense (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                         
1. (3) gesticulate, gesture, motion -- (show, express or direct through movement; "He gestured his desire to leave")
